    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯在拉斯维加斯市政厅就价格和移民问题受到追问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/harris-pressed-on-prices-immigration-in-las-vegas-town-hall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯周四在与环球电视网举行的市政厅会议上为自己在移民和医疗保健方面的记录进行辩护，以巩固她在拉丁裔选民中的地位，并抵制共和党人唐纳德·特朗普在关键的民主党阵营中的进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/harris-pressed-on-prices-immigration-in-las-vegas-town-hall</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 21:52:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通称特朗普贬值美元的举措将面临障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/trump-s-bid-to-weaken-dollar-would-face-hurdles-jpmorgan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通表示，独立的美联储和其他国家缺乏合作可能会挫败唐纳德·特朗普第二届政府削弱美元的潜在努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/trump-s-bid-to-weaken-dollar-would-face-hurdles-jpmorgan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 21:22:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>霍楚尔否认她计划帮助史蒂夫·科恩的纽约赌场的报道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/hochul-denies-report-she-plans-to-help-steve-cohen-s-nyc-casino</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州州长凯西·霍楚尔否认了有关她计划为亿万富翁史蒂夫·科恩（她的政治捐助者之一）在皇后区花旗球场旁边建造一个赌场和娱乐中心的报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/hochul-denies-report-she-plans-to-help-steve-cohen-s-nyc-casino</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 20:33:48 GMT</pubDate>
