    <item>
      <title>马斯克和特朗普煽动的虚假信息给飓风恢复增添压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/election-disinformation-stirred-by-musk-and-trump-strains-hurricane-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州和联邦官员已经在努力应对东南部接连发生的飓风，造成数百人死亡，现在又要应对另一个与灾难相关的威胁：有关救援工作和风暴成因的虚假信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/election-disinformation-stirred-by-musk-and-trump-strains-hurricane-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 19:30:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登要求国会重新审议米尔顿援助法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/biden-asks-congress-to-return-for-aid-bill-after-milton-landfall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，国会应该在休会期间返回通过紧急救援方案。飓风米尔顿隔夜袭击佛罗里达州墨西哥湾沿岸，造成数百万人断电，并引发龙卷风，造成至少 10 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/biden-asks-congress-to-return-for-aid-bill-after-milton-landfall</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 18:34:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国打击大型企业和富人以削减“巨额”债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/french-economy-latest-france-taxes-companies-wealthy-to-tackle-debt-pile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府公布了明年的预算，旨在投入 606 亿欧元（662 亿美元）来弥补公共财政的不足，重建投资者信心，尽管法国政府有可能被敌对的议会驱逐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/french-economy-latest-france-taxes-companies-wealthy-to-tackle-debt-pile</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普力推汽车贷款税收减免 力挺汽车业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/trump-to-propose-making-car-loan-interest-fully-tax-deductible</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普誓言将通过使汽车贷款利息完全免税并与墨西哥和加拿大重新谈判贸易协议来促进美国汽车业的发展，以争取摇摆州密歇根州的商业领袖和工人的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/trump-to-propose-making-car-loan-interest-fully-tax-deductible</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 17:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列安全内阁召开会议讨论伊朗问题，拜登呼吁谨慎行事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/israel-security-cabinet-to-meet-on-iran-as-biden-urges-restraint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列安全内阁周四晚间召开会议，讨论如何对伊朗上周的导弹袭击进行报复，但美国影响该决定的努力仍存在疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/israel-security-cabinet-to-meet-on-iran-as-biden-urges-restraint</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:33:12 GMT</pubDate>
